     "🧁 Chebab — Emirati pancakes with date syrup and cream cheese",
     "🍳 Balaleet — sweet vermicelli with egg and cardamom (breakfast)",
     "☕ Karak Tea — spiced milk tea, the everyday Emirati drink",
     "🐟 Hamour Fish — local Gulf white fish, usually grilled simply",
     "🫙 Madrooba — spiced fish and rice (coastal tradition)",
     "🍰 Umm Ali — bread pudding with cream, nuts and raisins",
     "🌾 Margoog — slow-cooked lamb and vegetable stew over thin bread",
     "🧄 Saloona — spiced stew, the everyday family meal",
